{
  "texts": [
    "Our goal is to examine the various ways in which MCDM techniques have been used to study diabetes and present an innovative categorization of their applications in this field.",
    "Figure 1 demonstrates the graphical abstract of the paper.",
    "Methods Search StrategiesA query was carried out on PubMed, Elsevier, Embase, MEDLINE, Scopus, MBC, Springer, IEEE, MDPI, Taylor and Francis Online, and Google Scholar based on published articles.",
    "The keywords for our paper were extracted from Medical Subject Headings (MeSH).",
    "The keywords \"diabetes\" and \"glucose\" were combined with MCDM techniques terms such as TOPSIS, AHP, and multi-criteria-decision-making using the Boolean operator AND/OR."
  ]
}